# pyBlindRL

This repository implements blind Richardson-Lucy deconvolution [1] using a PyTorch-based pipeline.

[1] D. A. Fish, A. M. Brinicombe, E. R. Pike, and J. G. Walker, "Blind deconvolution by means of the Richardsonâ€“Lucy algorithm," J. Opt. Soc. Am. A 12, 58-65 (1995).

